name: self portrait #1
description: imagine chaos. imagine unending energy. imagine ideas merging in on ideas, plans and plots pumping through your veins. imagine oscar the grouch. jim carrey as the grinch. imagine danny phantom. imagine a block of frozen spinach being strained of its ice cold juices, wrapped in a soggy paper towel - and not even a quilted one; some great value paper towel. unravel the paper towel and there you have me, with soggy torn bits of great value paper towel stuck on me.  this is me in 2021. let's see what next year brings.
